{"tid":769692,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"想貼錢買難受既就入一入黎","createTime":"2018-08-06T11:21:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-06T12:35:53.000Z","uid":38554,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"2aa6cf4d7d3818ff1f6103290d360beddad158a5","tid":769692,"uid":38554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T11:21:23.000Z","msg":"事緣四、五日之前去深水埗一間髮型屋整頭髮<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/06/190206_b9df627a6f32f6f7bbfd8ba027de2c00.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F06%2F190206_b9df627a6f32f6f7bbfd8ba027de2c00.png&h=777703fa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n我就買咗右手邊左上角 $450個plan<br />\n一入去我話我頭曾經染過黑色 佢哋就話好大機會再染都上唔到色 咁我明白既<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">重點就黎啦！！</span><br />\n我揀好個曲髮後 出到黎效果同我想要既已經有出入 都算<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">隔咗一日之後個頭直撚到仆街</span><br />\n<br />\n到今日我再去 佢哋全程係度話我無知識唔識keep個頭先會咁<br />\n我話我有keep有吹 佢哋係度話我講大話 <br />\n我電過幾次頭髮 就算唔keep都唔會完撚全係直<br />\n<br />\n佢哋四、五個staff 一齊係度笑我 話我有問題<br />\n話個頭咁樣係正常<br />\n完全講到係我責任咁<br />\n無啦啦比班人係度侮辱<br />\n<br />\n岩岩係間店洗完吹完後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/06/191104_b9d2a32256f9231357f83199c6d3bea6.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F06%2F191104_b9d2a32256f9231357f83199c6d3bea6.png&h=47b1e017&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢哋都堅持係我問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n地址: 九龍深水埗欽州街43號A地下<br />\n電話: 9203 0129<br />\n<br />\n唔好意思因爲想多d人見到所以post咗係創意台"},{"pid":"19783bffb2a425c6b5c8501cd8f59c1f1d27bfc6","tid":769692,"uid":171816,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-06T11:24:52.000Z","msg":"幻想圖係點？"},{"pid":"ccac92de3c1bd8f49a9f3ad05ca393d973beba73","t